request.description:
Search product model numbers.
**Auth:** Bearer token required (`Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}`).

**Request Body:**
```json
{
  "search": "IF"
}
```

**Example Response:**
```json
[
  {
    "model_no": "IF-001"
  },
  {
    "model_no": "IF-002"
  }
]
```

